text: Pro-Death Ravers is the second album by the Danish band Psychopomps. It was originally released in 1993 and differs greatly from their previous release. This album has a greater focus on guitars and less focus on synthesizers. ==Track listing== ==Personnel== Jesper Schmidt: Vox, Programming, Keyboards Flemming Norre Larsen: Programming, Lyrics ==External links== * Psychopomps at myspace * Pro-Death Ravers CD at Amazon.com Category:1993 albums Category:Psychopomps (band) albums
